  "content": "<div class=\"stat-box\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-purple);\">0</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\">Design rewrites</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Second example -->\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-cyan); padding: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom: 12px;\">Another Example: BM25 Hybrid Search</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;\">\n      \"Recall is 37.5%\" became 7 issues across 4 phases with measurable ship gates: Source Recall@5 > 50%, MRR > 0.60, p95 latency < 20ms. Parallel phases identified. Implementation not started yet. The board is ready.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>Zero rewrites because the design was validated before code existed. The 5-persona review caught flaws in the spec, not in the implementation.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">08 / 09</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 9: TAKEAWAYS -->\n<div class=\"slide\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f172a 0%, #1a2332 50%, #0f172a 100%);\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Key Takeaways</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 36px;\">\n    What Actually<br>Matters\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128161;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;\">The thinking is the hard part</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.5;\">\n          Layer 1 is where I learn. Exploring trade-offs, challenging assumptions, making judgment calls. The implementation is the easy part.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>",
